<item>
            <title>[HADOOP-7389] Use of TestingGroups by tests causes subsequent tests to fail</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HADOOP-7389</link>
                <project id="12310240" key="HADOOP">Hadoop Common</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;As mentioned in &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HADOOP-6671&quot; title=&quot;To use maven for hadoop common builds&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;HADOOP-6671&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;HADOOP-6671&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;tt&gt;UserGroupInformation.createUserForTesting(...)&lt;/tt&gt; manipulates static state which can cause test cases which are run after a call to this function to fail.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12510251">HADOOP-7389</key>
            <summary>Use of TestingGroups by tests causes subsequent tests to fail</summary>
